[SPEAKER_24]: So today we're at the Westwood Rec Center and today we're doing a pool party that we host annually every summer.

12:14.949 --> 12:31.360
[SPEAKER_24]: We're working with Council District 5 and we're here to support the West LA community and basically what we do, we introduce them to our Learn to Swim programs, our small crafts programs and today we have a fortunate opportunity to introduce our Wibbit that they're utilizing and they're having a blast.

