[SPEAKER_24]: We have a small craft program where we introduce learn to surf, learn to paddle, and then we also do learn to kayak.

12:39.725 --> 12:47.121
[SPEAKER_24]: So, you know, giving the community members an opportunity to see those that they don't normally see, and it gets them more prepped for open bodies of water.

12:49.801 --> 12:53.104
